<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>todai</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-B0vP5xmATw1+K9KRQjQERJvTumQW0nPEzvF6L/Z6nronJ3oUOFUFpCjEUQouq2+l" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
        <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/stars/stars.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/styles.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/home.css"/>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Courgette&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-DyZ88mC6Up2uqS4h/KRgHuoeGwBcD4Ng9SiP4dIRy0EXTlnuz47vAwmeGwVChigm" crossorigin="anonymous">

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bs-custom-file-input/dist/bs-custom-file-input.min.js"></script>

    </head>
    <body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100">
            <%- include("./partials/navbar") %>    
        <main class="container-fluid paper mb-0 pb-0">
            <div class="mt-3 ml-2 mb-0 position-fixed">
                <%- include("./partials/flash") %>    
            </div>
            <div class="container mt-5 mb-0">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h1>How's your <%=today %>?</h1>
                            <!-- <p class="text-center font-weight-bold">──────<span class="text-warning">★</span>──────</p> -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col wrapper justify-content-center ">
                            <input name="ratingRadio" type="radio" id="st1" value="1" />
                            <label for="st1"></label>
                            <input name="ratingRadio" type="radio" id="st2" value="2" />
                            <label for="st2"></label>
                            <input name="ratingRadio" type="radio" id="st3" value="3" />
                            <label for="st3"></label>
                            <input name="ratingRadio" type="radio" id="st4" value="4" />
                            <label for="st4"></label>
                            <input name="ratingRadio" type="radio" id="st5" value="5" />
                            <label for="st5"></label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col mb-3">
                        <textarea disabled style="resize: none" class="blinking-cursor d-block border mx-auto rounded border-dark" cols="20" row="70">|</textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row justify-content-center mb-4">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline btn-warning d-block my-3 "><a href="/register" class="text-dark">Sign Up</a></button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline btn-dark d-block ml-3 my-3"><a href="/login" class="text-light">Login</a></button>
                </div>
                <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-7 text-center bg-light p-3">
                        <h4 class="">meet <strong style="font-family: 'Courgette" class="text-warning">todai<sup style="font-size: 12px">&copy</sup></strong></h4>
                        <h6 class="">A quick self-reflection tool & the world's first collective online journal</h6>
                        <!-- <a href="/data" class="text-decoration-none">Explore more</a> -->
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container-fluid px-5 pr-0 mt-4 mb-0 pt-3 pb-0">
                    <div class="row mb-5 features">
                        <!-- Column -->
                        <div class="col text-center border-right pl-5">
                            <div class="icon-round align-items-center"><i class="far fa-calendar-alt text-warning"></i></div>
                            <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Quick self-reflection</h5>
                            <p class="">Todai allows you to practice self-reflection in a quick, easy way. Rate your day on a scale of 1-5. If you have time, jot down a few thoughts. Over time, with daily self-reflection, you'll gain a clearer picture of your weeks, months and years.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col text-center border-right">
                            <div class="icon-round" style="height: 80px"><i class=""><i class="fas fa-globe text-warning"></i></i></div>
                            <h5 class="font-weight-bold">A global perspective</h5>
                            <p class="">Read through the latest anonymous Todai entries from all around the world and maybe how you feel about your day will change. A global perspective allows us to cultivate gratitude and aspire towards a better tomorrow.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col text-center border-right">
                            <div class="icon-round"><i class="fas fa-chart-line text-warning"></i></div>
                            <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Data-driven</h5>
                            <p class="">We believe in healthy social comparison that is honest and data-driven. Track your own ratings over time (always private) and view local or global average ratings in real-time. Filter ratings by country, age, or gender or view the top trending keywords for today.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col  text-center pr-5">
                            <div class="icon-round "><i class="far fa-bell-slash text-warning"></i></div>
                            <h5 class="font-weight-bold">No addiction</h5>
                            <p class="">Todai is a minimalist social-network. No followers. No notifications. No likes. No endless timeline. AKA, no addiction. You can only post once a day and we encourage anonymity to protect the integrity of all ratings. Todai is designed to help us connect to ourselves and to each other, without the toxicity. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <%- include("./partials/footer") %>
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-Piv4xVNRyMGpqkS2by6br4gNJ7DXjqk09RmUpJ8jgGtD7zP9yug3goQfGII0yAns" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src='/javascripts/validateForms.js'></script>
